How It Works
1. Template Creation (On Device)
Raw neural node data → Feature extraction (on device)

Features are NORMALIZED (0-1 range)

Raw data is DISCARDED after extraction

Template is CRYPTOGRAPHICALLY SIGNED

2. Template Sharing (Person Controls)
Person chooses which features to share

Person sets permission level

Person selects which models can access

Person can REVOKE anytime

3. Marketing Models Receive
Receive ONLY sanitized features

Cannot reverse-engineer identity

Cannot access raw neural data

Template is VERIFIABLE (signature check)

4. Multiple Models, Same Template
One template serves ALL marketing models

Person doesn't need multiple templates

Each model gets SAME anonymized features

Models use features for their specific purpose

Security Properties
Property	How It Works
Non-reversible	Features are mathematical derivatives, not raw data
Person-controlled	Person grants/revokes access on their device
Cryptographic verification	Signatures prevent tampering
Time-limited	Templates expire
Model-specific tokens	Each model gets unique access token
No cross-model identification	Models cannot combine templates to identify person
Marketing Use Cases
Model Type	Uses Template Features For
Ad Optimizer	Attention score → adjust bid price
Content Recommender	Engagement level → suggest content
Audience Segmenter	Region + attention → segment audiences
Personalization Engine	Product interest → personalize offers
A/B Testing	Emotional valence → measure response
This system ensures the person's RAW neural data NEVER leaves their device while still enabling powerful marketing applications through DERIVED, ANONYMIZED templates.
